      ],
      "right": "275px"
    },
    {
      "width": "377px",
      "text": "עיניו: <b><big>מתני'</big></b> <i data-commentator=\"Mishneh Torah, Prayer and the Priestly Blessing\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Sefer Mitzvot Gadol\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Tur\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i>מזכירין גבורות",
